EduTrack Lite is a lightweight course enrollment and tracking API built with FastAPI. It allows users to register, enroll in courses, track completion, and manage course offerings â€” all using in-memory storage and Pydantic validation.

 Features
- User Management
- Create, read, update, delete users
- Deactivate users
- Course Management
- Create, read, update, delete courses
- Close course enrollment
- View enrolled users per course
- Enrollment Management
- Enroll active users in open courses
- Prevent duplicate enrollments
- Mark course completion
- View enrollments by user or globally

 Tech Stack
- FastAPI for API framework
- Pydantic for data validation
- Uvicorn as ASGI server
- Pytest + TestClient for testing
- In-memory storage (lists/dicts)
